'''Sara Dylan''' is an actress based in Ireland. She starred in the independent film ''Fiddler's Walk'' in 2006. In 2009 she appeared in the canabalistic slasher film ''Gnaw''.

In ''[[Game of Thrones]]'' she is playing the role of a [[Unidentified handmaiden|hand maid]]. She joined the cast as a guest star in the [[Season 2|second season]] and continued in the [[Season 3|third]] and [[Season 4|fourth]] seasons.
